Package com.github.davidmoten.rx.jdbc

Database querying utilities for use with JDBC and RxJava.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConnectionProvider
    Provides JDBC Connections as required.
    Query
    A database DML query, either update/insert or select.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectionProviderFromUrl
    Provides Connections from a url (using DriverManager.getConnection()).
    ConnectionProviderPooled
    Provides database connection pooling using c3p0.
    Database
    Main entry point for manipulations of a database using rx-java-jdbc style queries.
    Database.Builder
    Builds a Database.
    QueryBuilder
    Builds base information for a query (either select or update).
    QuerySelect
    A query and its executable context.
    QuerySelect.Builder
    Builds a QuerySelect.
    QuerySelect.OperatorBuilder<R>
    Builder pattern for select query Observable.Operator.
    QuerySelectOperator<T,R>
    Operator corresponding to the QuerySelectOperation.
    QueryUpdate
    Always emits an Observable of size 1 containing the number of affected records.
    QueryUpdate.Builder
    Builds a QueryUpdate.
    QueryUpdateOperator<R>
    Observable.Operator corresonding to QueryUpdateOperation.
    Util
    Utility methods.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OperatorType
    The types of Observable.Operator that can be created by a select or update query.
